1) Donwload JDK 1.8 *

2) Donwload Apache Tomcat 8

3) Downlaod STS Editor
https://spring.io/tools/sts/all

4) Install XAMPP Package
https://www.apachefriends.org/download.html

5) Spring Hibernate Integration
http://howtodoinjava.com/spring/spring-orm/spring-3-and-hibernate-integration-tutorial-with-example/

6) Database :
    Login : (for all)
        1. user_role - id, role
        2. user_logins - id, username/ emailId, password, first_name, last_name 
        3. user_registration - rest fields (image, address, personal info)
        
7) Versions :
    MySQL - Latest Version 
    Spring - 4.0.2
    Hibernate - 4
        